HEADWORD: Sublimification
<hw>Sub*lim`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sublimis</ets> sublime + <ets>-ficare</ets> to make. See
<er>-ry</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of making sublime, or state of being
made sublime.</def>⟦br⟧
